summary: Cambridge physics graduate with Ph.D. in Electron Optics. Postdoc work also on applications of high power lasers. Worked for Philips for 27 years in development of electron microscopes, household magnetrons and MRI magnet systems. Started field archeology on retirement and after 15 years of active excavation moved to research on the history of local Eindhoven institutions.
